OL,3,CTraffic stop catches on-the-run
OL,4,Cfraudster who stole over #1million
OL,6,FA Dumfries man who stole multiple
OL,7,Fidentities and accumulated more than
OL,8,F#1million in false bank accounts has
OL,9,Fbeen imprisoned for four years.
OL,11,FCraig Milligan, 47, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fcharges of identity theft and being
OL,13,Finvolved in a fraudulent scheme at
OL,14,FGlasgow High Court.
OL,16,FMilligan used the identities of two
OL,17,Fdead men and various other aliases to
OL,18,Ffraudulently open accounts and obtain
OL,19,Fcredit cards.
