OL,4,Cfraudster who stole over #1million
OL,6,FHe had previously gone missing in
OL,7,F2010, when he was due to be sentenced
OL,8,Ffor fraud charges and faced an
OL,9,Findecent images accusation.
OL,11,FThe fraudster, who held dual Canadian
OL,12,Fand British nationality, was finally
OL,13,Fcaught in October 2024, when he was
OL,14,Fstopped by police officers in his car
OL,15,Fand provided a driving licence in the
OL,16,Fname of Daniel Pindell.
