OL,4,Cfraudster who stole over #1million
OL,6,FOfficers later discovered that Mr
OL,7,FPindell's identity belonged to a man
OL,8,Ffrom Florida who had died in 2009,
OL,9,Fwhile further investigations revealed
OL,10,Fthis alias was linked to a man from
OL,11,FLimerick, Thomas Warren, who had died
OL,12,Fin Dallas in 2010.
OL,14,FPolice went on to search Milligan's
OL,15,Fhouse and discovered equipment used to
OL,16,Fmake false IDs including scanners,
OL,17,Fprinters, ultraviolet lights and
OL,18,Fholograms, and #10,000 in cash.
