OL,6,FThis led to police finding Milligan
OL,7,Fhad illegally opened seven bank
OL,8,Faccounts and six credit cards using
OL,9,Fthe aliases.
OL,11,FA total of #1,092,998.04 had been paid
OL,12,Finto Milligan's bank accounts between
OL,13,FMay 2012 and January 2025, including
OL,14,Fnearly #300,000 in cryptocurrency
OL,15,Fpayments.
OL,17,FHe will now be subject to confiscation
OL,18,Faction under Proceeds of Crime
OL,19,Flegislation to recover monies obtained
OL,20,Fillegally.
