OL,6,F"For offences of this gravity, only a
OL,7,Fprison sentence is appropriate."
OL,9,FSineidin Corrins, Procurator Fiscal at
OL,10,Fthe Crown Office and Procurator Fiscal
OL,11,FService, said: "Craig Milligan has
OL,12,Fbeen brought to justice for a
OL,13,Fcalculated and long-running fraud.
OL,15,F"He callously stole personal and
OL,16,Fconfidential information and used this
OL,17,Fto fraudulently obtain bank accounts
OL,18,Fand credit.
